  "id": "php/deletearrayitems",
  "contentHtml": "<h1>Delete Array Items</h1>\n<p>You can use the array_splice() function.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>array_splice(variable, start, length)</li>\n</ul>\n<pre><code class=\"language-php\"><span class=\"hljs-meta\">&#x3C;?php</span>\n\n<span class=\"hljs-variable\">$cars</span> = [<span class=\"hljs-string\">'Lexus'</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">'Toyota'</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">'Honda'</span>];\n<span class=\"hljs-title function_ invoke__\">array_splice</span>(<span class=\"hljs-variable\">$cars</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>);\n\n<span class=\"hljs-meta\">?></span>\n</code></pre>\n<p>It automatically reindexes the array.</p>\n<h2>unset()</h2>\n<p>Also deletes existing array items.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>But does not re-arrange indexes.</li>\n</ul>\n<pre><code class=\"language-php\"><span class=\"hljs-meta\">&#x3C;?php</span>\n\n<span class=\"hljs-variable\">$cars</span> = [<span class=\"hljs-string\">'Honda'</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">'Toyota'</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">'Chevy'</span>];\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">unset</span>(<span class=\"hljs-variable\">$cars</span>[<span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>]);\n\n<span class=\"hljs-meta\">?></span>\n</code></pre>\n<h2>Remove Multiple Array Items</h2>\n<p>Same idea.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Except unset() takes multiple arguments.</li>\n</ul>\n<pre><code class=\"language-php\"><span class=\"hljs-meta\">&#x3C;?php</span>\n\n<span class=\"hljs-variable\">$cars</span> = [<span class=\"hljs-string\">'Honda'</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">'Toyota'</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">'Chevy'</span>];\n<span class=\"hljs-title function_ invoke__\">array_splice</span>(<span class=\"hljs-variable\">$cars</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>);\n\n<span class=\"hljs-variable\">$foods</span> = [<span class=\"hljs-string\">'Pizza'</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">'Pasta'</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">'Burger'</span>];\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">unset</span>(<span class=\"hljs-variable\">$foods</span>[<span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>], <span class=\"hljs-variable\">$foods</span>[<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>]);\n\n<span class=\"hljs-meta\">?></span>\n</code></pre>\n<h2>Remove Item From an Associative Array</h2>\n<p>Use the unset() function.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Specify the key of the item to delete.</li>\n</ul>\n<pre><code class=\"language-php\"><span class=\"hljs-meta\">&#x3C;?php</span>\n\n<span class=\"hljs-variable\">$cars</span> = [\n    <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"Honda\"</span> => <span class=\"hljs-number\">1000</span>,\n    <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"Toyota\"</span> => <span class=\"hljs-number\">1200</span>,\n    <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"Lexus\"</span> => <span class=\"hljs-number\">1400</span>\n];\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">unset</span>(<span class=\"hljs-variable\">$cars</span>[<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"Honda\"</span>]);\n\n<span class=\"hljs-meta\">?></span>\n</code></pre>\n<h2>array_diff()</h2>\n<p>You can also use the array_diff() function.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>array_diff(variable, values)</li>\n<li>Takes the values, not keys as parameters.</li>\n</ul>\n<pre><code class=\"language-php\"><span class=\"hljs-meta\">&#x3C;?php</span>\n\n<span class=\"hljs-variable\">$cars</span> = [\n    <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"Toyota\"</span> => <span class=\"hljs-number\">1000</span>,\n    <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"Honda\"</span> => <span class=\"hljs-number\">1200</span>,\n    <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"Lexus\"</span> => <span class=\"hljs-number\">1400</span>\n];\n<span class=\"hljs-title function_ invoke__\">array_diff</span>(<span class=\"hljs-variable\">$cars</span>, [<span class=\"hljs-number\">1000</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">1200</span>]);\n\n<span class=\"hljs-meta\">?></span>\n</code></pre>\n<h2>Remove Last Item</h2>\n<p>Use array_pop().</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-php\"><span class=\"hljs-meta\">&#x3C;?php</span>\n\n<span class=\"hljs-variable\">$cars</span> = [<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"Honda\"</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"Toyota\"</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"Chevy\"</span>];\n<span class=\"hljs-title function_ invoke__\">array_pop</span>(<span class=\"hljs-variable\">$cars</span>);\n\n<span class=\"hljs-meta\">?></span>\n</code></pre>\n<h2>Remove First Item</h2>\n<p>Use array_shift().</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-php\"><span class=\"hljs-meta\">&#x3C;?php</span>\n\n<span class=\"hljs-variable\">$cars</span> = [<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"Honda\"</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"Toyota\"</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"Chevy\"</span>];\n<span class=\"hljs-title function_ invoke__\">array_shift</span>(<span class=\"hljs-variable\">$cars</span>);\n\n<span class=\"hljs-meta\">?></span>\n</code></pre>",
